&lt;BLOCKQUOTE style=&quot;PADDING-LEFT: 5px; MARGIN-LEFT: 5px; BORDER-LEFT: #1010ff 2px solid&quot;&gt;&lt;TT&gt;Yggdrasil: We&#39;re still discussing details, but I&#39;ll report back very&lt;BR&gt;soon. Prime out.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;He frowned in a way that was very similar as that of his infamous&lt;BR&gt;Autobot ancestor. Kup&#39;s team was good, but it exposed them too much,&lt;BR&gt;he thought.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Yggdrasil: I don&#39;t like the idea that all three highest officers here,&lt;BR&gt;meaning you, Rodimus and me, get to go. It will be a drawback if the&lt;BR&gt;preds decide to move out just then. I suggest that Rodimus stays and&lt;BR&gt;that we replace him with either Empath or Blackfang, or even one of&lt;BR&gt;the new guys around.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;--- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, Richard Allen &lt;roborick007@y...&gt; wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; : : Rodimus Prime : :&lt;BR&gt;&gt; Rodimus holds her close, tickling her, while he takes care of business.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; He opens a comm.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; Rodimus Prime: Yggdrasil, what&#39;s the status of that team?&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; Airshadow Nightstar &lt;airly2002@h...&gt; wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; Elita:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; Elita continued giggling and laughting. She was enjoying a lot&lt;BR&gt;playing with her daddy. She was having a lot fun and if she would be a&lt;BR&gt;little older, she would have wished that it never ends.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;Reply-To: nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com &gt;To: nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com&lt;BR&gt;&gt;Subject: Re: Daddy &gt;Date: Sat, 10 May 2003 21:59:17 -0700 (PDT) &gt; &gt;:&lt;BR&gt;: Rodimus Prime : : &gt;Rodimus was having fun playing with his daughter,&lt;BR&gt;but his thoughts started to dwell on Nightlight. He wished she was&lt;BR&gt;there so they could all be together as a family. &gt; &gt;Rodimus tossed&lt;BR&gt;Elita up just a little bit, then cought her. &gt; &gt; &gt;Airshadow Nightstar&lt;BR&gt;wrote: &gt;Elita: &gt; &gt;Elita Laughtes Aloud, that was such fun. She was&lt;BR&gt;gigglig pleaced while she spread her little arms toward her dad &gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt;From: Richard Allen &gt;Reply-To: nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com &gt;To:&lt;BR&gt;nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com &gt;Subject: Re: Daddy &gt;Date: Sat, 10 May 2003&lt;BR&gt;21:27:31 -0700 (PDT) &gt; &gt;: : Rodimus Prime : : &gt;Rodimus looks stunned&lt;BR&gt;after getting hit in the nose. &gt; &gt;Rodimus Prime: I got your hand, but&lt;BR&gt;you got daddy&#39;s nose. &gt; &gt;Rodimus raises her over his head and spins&lt;BR&gt;around twice. &gt; &gt; &gt;airly2000 wrote:Elita: &gt; &gt;Elita laughted more and&lt;BR&gt;without liked with her jerking movement she &gt;struck slighty her&lt;BR&gt;daddy&#39;s nose &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;--- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, Richard Allen&lt;BR&gt;&gt;wrote: &gt; &gt; : : Rodimus Prime : : &gt; &gt; Rodimus traps two of her fingers&lt;BR&gt;in his mouth, playing around. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus Prime: I got your hand,&lt;BR&gt;what&#39;cha gunna do? &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; airly2000 wrote:Elita: &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Elita&lt;BR&gt;giggled a lot, she touched with one of her little hand his &gt; &gt; daddy&#39;s&lt;BR&gt;chin. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; --- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, Richard&lt;BR&gt;Allen &gt;wrote: &gt; &gt; &gt; : : Rodimus Prime : : &gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus picks up his&lt;BR&gt;daughter, holding her close. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus Prime: I can tell&lt;BR&gt;that you are going to be a strong girl. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; airly2000&lt;BR&gt;wrote:Elita: &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Eliata laughted and giggled more she spread&lt;BR&gt;her little arms &gt;towards &gt; &gt; &gt; her daddy. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; --- In&lt;BR&gt;nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, Richard Allen &gt; &gt; wrote: &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; : : Rodimus&lt;BR&gt;Prime : : &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus looked at his fully transformed daughter. He&lt;BR&gt;could see &gt; &gt; the &gt; &gt; &gt; influences from Nightlight and himself. &gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus Prime: Now you see your true form hunny. You are a &gt;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; cybertroian transformer. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; airly2000&lt;BR&gt;wrote:Elita: &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Elita started to laught more and more.&lt;BR&gt;Sometimes, by seconds, &gt; &gt; &gt; seemed &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; that her little chest&lt;BR&gt;would open to show the rest of her robot &gt; &gt; &gt; mode. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; At last,&lt;BR&gt;that help her to complete her tranform. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; She looked&lt;BR&gt;extraordinary like her mommy, but with several &gt;things &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; that&lt;BR&gt;she heired from her daddy: Her metallic skin was like &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;BR&gt;Nightlight&#39;s, her robot mode mixed Golden, red and copper. Her &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;BR&gt;helmet was like Rodimu&#39;s; her eyes were like his father and &gt;like &gt; &gt;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; Nightlight, her face, arms and leg had silver. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;BR&gt;Elita was amazing about her hands and feet, she looked &gt;facinated &gt; &gt;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; how &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; her fingers moved. Her tranformation and look were&lt;BR&gt;almost as &gt;her &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; mom; but she and anyone didn&#39;t know by now,&lt;BR&gt;that her behavior &gt; &gt; would &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; be as his dad. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; --- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, Richard Allen &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; wrote: &gt; &gt;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; : : Rodimus Prime : : &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; She was still in mid&lt;BR&gt;transformation so Rodimus tickles her &gt; &gt; again. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Maybe he&lt;BR&gt;could trigger the rest of the change. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;BR&gt;airly2000 wrote:Elita: &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; elita didn&#39;t understand&lt;BR&gt;what her daddy liked that she did. &gt;She &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; just &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; watched&lt;BR&gt;and continued looking her little legs... They moved, &gt; &gt; they &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; moved when she wished that moved then they belongs her... &gt;she &gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; looked &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; again at her daddy as she thought herself what will&lt;BR&gt;happen &gt;next. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; --- In&lt;BR&gt;nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, Richard Allen &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; wrote: &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; :&lt;BR&gt;: Rodimus Prime : : &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus had to laugh as his daughter&lt;BR&gt;was stuck in mid &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; transformation. He knew that she couldn&#39;t&lt;BR&gt;control it at such &gt;a &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; young &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; age. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; Rodimus Prime: Come on hunny, try a little harder. You &gt;almost &gt; &gt;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; have &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; it. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus tried to guide&lt;BR&gt;the movement of the parts so that &gt;she &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; would &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; catch&lt;BR&gt;on, and finish the sequence herself. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; airly2000 wrote:Elita: &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Elita laughted more&lt;BR&gt;while she was trying to caught &gt;Rodimus&#39; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; hand, &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; she&lt;BR&gt;suddenly sneezed; that did that half of her little &gt;body &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;BR&gt;transformed and small and little legs showed. It seemed &gt;that &gt